1
00:01:15,440 --> 00:01:18,120
Strip these two dancers.

2
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:22,320
Let go!

3
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:26,440
Gently.

4
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:28,400
You're hurting the girls.

5
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,440
Miss,

6
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:39,960
where did you learn your martial arts?

7
00:01:40,759 --> 00:01:42,000
As far as I know,

8
00:01:42,520 --> 00:01:45,200
Qihong Tower only teaches the Five Rites and Six Arts.

9
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:47,360
It doesn't include the Five Archery and Five Charioteering skills,

10
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,440
let alone

11
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,520
teaching you martial arts.

12
00:01:53,039 --> 00:01:53,840
My Lord,

13
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:57,400
my father was a military officer.

14
00:01:58,360 --> 00:02:01,400
Because he was involved in a major case ten years ago,

15
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:06,400
all the men in my family were exiled.

16
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:10,800
Ladies,

17
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:13,120
please tell me separately,

18
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:15,720
when did you each enter Qihong Tower?

19
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,800
I entered Qihong Tower at sixteen.

20
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,760
It has been five years.

21
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:23,640
That should be the 17th year of Shengyuan.

22
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:25,650
The following year,

23
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:28,000
I became one of the top courtesans here.

24
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,560
And you?

25
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,040
Although I am from the Western Regions,

26
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:34,400
I settled in the Central Plains with my parents as a child.

27
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:37,120
I entered Qihong Tower in the 19th year of Shengyuan.

28
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,240
I am older,

29
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:40,660
so I've always been an unnoticed dancer.

30
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:47,640
Miss,

31
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:50,120
how old are you?

32
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:53,440
I was born in the 32nd year of Tianxu.

33
00:02:54,720 --> 00:03:00,120
Is this how the Censorate handles things?

34
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:05,200
Then when did you enter Qihong Tower?

35
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:08,160
Why did you say you were old?

36
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:11,040
I was twenty-one at the time.

37
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:14,300
I really couldn't compare to the other sisters.

38
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:16,040
My Lords,

39
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:17,440
to solve this case,

40
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:19,840
I need an important item.

41
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:23,000
It must be in the Young Marquis's study.

42
00:03:24,440 --> 00:03:27,160
Pihu, Miss Gu,

43
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,820
go get it for me at once.

44
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:29,960
Yes.

45
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:34,440
I'll go with you.

46
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:38,240
Your Northern Office

47
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,970
is full of confidential files.

48
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,800
If she touches something she shouldn't,

49
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,660
I can't take the responsibility.

50
00:03:56,079 --> 00:03:57,200
This jade pendant,

51
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:58,800
where did you get it?

52
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:02,560
What does it have to do with Lord Su Ziliang?

53
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,400
I got this...

54
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:06,760
when I ran an errand for someone.

55
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,440
He didn't have money to pay,

56
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:10,640
so he gave me this to settle the debt.

57
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:13,100
Aren't you afraid I'll expose you

58
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,240
and punish you?

59
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:18,000
Since you saved me earlier, My Lord,

60
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:20,660
I assume you won't contradict yourself now.

61
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,720
Now that the case is clear,

62
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:26,520
please don't make things difficult for me.

63
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:29,000
The case is clear?

64
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,760
How so?

65
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:34,330
There are no pure courtesans in Qihong Tower.

66
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:36,690
The dancer's reaction was obviously off.

67
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:39,880
The courtesan could clearly state her birth year.

68
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:43,380
From the late Emperor's reign to the Tianxu era,

69
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:47,800
it should be 34 minus 32,

70
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,560
plus the Shengyuan years.

71
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:51,320
That leaves a one-year gap.

72
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:54,720
She knows nothing about our dynasty's calendar.

73
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:57,000
It means she hasn't lived in the Central Plains for long.

74
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:57,800
She is lying.

75
00:04:58,159 --> 00:05:01,560
What if she says it was long ago and she forgot?

76
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:03,440
We don't have hard evidence.

77
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:05,240
If we don't have evidence,

78
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:07,840
then we'll create some.

79
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:14,800
Rumor has it this paper was enchanted by the Imperial Preceptor.

80
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:18,120
As long as this paper is placed in the suspect's hand,

81
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,240
whoever is guilty,

82
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:22,520
the character for 'Sin' will appear on it,

83
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:23,880
signifying their sin.

84
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:31,240
It seems clear who the real culprit is.

85
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,900
You're trying to frame me.

86
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:37,200
This is a common Jianghu method for secret messages.

87
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:39,440
It requires special ink.

88
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,800
Once the ink dries,

89
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:42,080
the writing disappears.

90
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:44,440
It must be heated to reappear.

91
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:47,200
If I didn't know this Jianghu secret,

92
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:49,640
wouldn't I have been wrongfully executed by you?

93
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:52,720
This ink only appeared three months ago.

94
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:56,300
Even many in the Jianghu don't know about it.

95
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:59,400
Miss, you are from Qihong Tower.

96
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,280
How did you know about it?

97
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:08,800
Don't come closer, or I'll slit her throat.

98
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:12,720
You dare threaten an imperial official?

99
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,320
Seize her.

100
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:13,800
Yes.

101
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:58,200
The current Emperor is incompetent and cruel.

102
00:06:58,200 --> 00:07:00,840
Ten years ago, over a fabricated witchcraft case,

103
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:02,500
he slaughtered the innocent.

104
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:06,280
Now he deserves to suffer this chaos of witchcraft,

105
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:09,100
the retribution of a collapsing empire.

106
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:15,680
It's too late for you and them.

107
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,680
Dali is doomed.

108
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:42,880
What happened?

109
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:45,159
She must have been poisoned long ago,

110
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:46,360
and silenced.

111
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:48,680
Gu poison.

112
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,480
This is a Gu spell.

113
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:56,500
This person could control the poison's activation so precisely.

114
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:59,680
Their mastery of Gu is unparalleled.

115
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:01,330
Little Marquis.

116
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:03,400
The trail has gone cold again.

117
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:04,480
What should we do?

118
00:08:06,280 --> 00:08:09,080
Take all the maids and servants around this dancer

119
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:10,520
to the Imperial Prison.

120
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,680
Torture them.

121
00:08:13,520 --> 00:08:15,240
They must know something.

122
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:17,770
Let's go.

123
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,000
Lord Fang.

124
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:24,400
Fang Li.

125
00:08:24,400 --> 00:08:24,960
Lord Fang.

126
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:26,480
As for the torture,

127
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,880
do you want to go in and watch?

128
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:28,800
No need.

129
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:31,360
I have to return to my manor to write a memorial

130
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,480
to His Majesty.

131
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:35,039
I hope you handle this impartially

132
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:36,370
and solve the case soon.

133
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,280
Miss Gu.

134
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:45,240
Please.

135
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,960
Lord Fang, I'm sorry.

136
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,970
I suddenly have an urgent need.

137
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,780
I'll go relieve myself first.

138
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:36,900
Zhao, haven't seen you in a while.

139
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:46,880
Boss, give me a few more flatbreads.

140
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:48,720
Alright, wait a moment.

141
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:49,800
Coming right up.

142
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,600
You're here.

143
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,240
Come here.

144
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,040
Have you eaten?

145
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:02,570
Come, have some flatbread.

146
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,920
Here, there's enough for everyone.

147
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:05,480
Here.

148
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,240
One for you.

149
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:09,080
Everyone gets one.

150
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,760
It's so good.

151
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,080
It's delicious.

152
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,040
Oh no.

153
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:22,360
Help!

154
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:25,800
Save us!

155
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:30,240
Lord Fang, we'll meet again.

156
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:39,240
Who exactly is she?

157
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:43,920
How dare she trick me together with Fang Ji?

158
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,370
Little Marquis.

159
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:50,920
The maid of the Young Marquis's dancer has confessed.

160
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:52,920
She revealed Huang Wansan's hiding place.

161
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:53,760
Well done.

162
00:10:53,920 --> 00:10:56,400
Take men to capture Huang Wansan immediately.

163
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:56,960
Yes, sir.

164
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:16,200
Brother Li.

165
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,340
Why are you in my house?

166
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,320
Come in, quickly.

167
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,400
Just come in.

168
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:22,940
What are you doing?

169
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:25,240
Zhaoxue, you have to save me.

170
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,280
What happened?

171
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,200
I just left Qihong Tower.

172
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,000
And I found out

173
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:34,640
the person the Dragon Guard is after is Huang Wansan.

174
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:35,800
You know Huang Wansan?

175
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:36,600
I do.

176
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:38,480
Huang Wansan is my client.

177
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:39,560
If he gets caught,

178
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:40,360
I...

179
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:44,560
Do you know where Huang Wansan is now?

180
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:45,520
I don't know.

181
00:11:45,920 --> 00:11:47,400
I've asked around.

182
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:50,480
The Dragon Guard is already on their way to arrest him.

183
00:11:51,800 --> 00:11:53,530
Is your information reliable?

184
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:56,400
When have I ever been wrong?

185
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:58,530
Why do you care about Huang Wansan?

186
00:11:58,560 --> 00:12:01,160
I heard this involves that witchcraft business again.

187
00:12:01,160 --> 00:12:02,160
Back then,

188
00:12:02,520 --> 00:12:05,720
didn't your family suffer enough because of witchcraft?

189
00:12:12,160 --> 00:12:12,760
So,

190
00:12:13,680 --> 00:12:14,960
did you find Yan'er?

191
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,560
Yan'er was taken.

192
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,000
Taken?

193
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,400
Kidnapped.

194
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:29,090
There were two forces in Qihong Tower at the time.

195
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:31,040
One was the Dragon Guard.

196
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:33,000
The other was Huang Wansan.

197
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:36,170
The Dragon Guard doesn't have Yan'er.

198
00:12:36,680 --> 00:12:37,600
Then Yan'er

199
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:40,890
must have fallen into the hands of Huang Wansan's group.

200
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:45,000
If the witchcraft case was really Huang Wansan's doing,

201
00:12:45,680 --> 00:12:46,560
could it be that back then,

202
00:12:46,560 --> 00:12:49,020
he was also involved in framing your father?

203
00:12:51,680 --> 00:12:54,200
Back then, my father ignored advice

204
00:12:54,560 --> 00:12:56,240
and insisted on investigating the witchcraft case.

205
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:58,040
He made countless enemies in court,

206
00:12:58,040 --> 00:12:59,700
leading to our family's ruin.

207
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:03,320
Even Yan'er was made a state slave.

208
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:09,000
As for my father,

209
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:11,760
I can't deal with it now.

210
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:13,090
I don't want to, either.

211
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:16,170
I just want to take Yan'er and run far away.

212
00:13:20,520 --> 00:13:21,280
Brother Li.

213
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:23,480
Do you know if Huang Wansan

214
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:25,810
has any trusted aides left in the capital?

215
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:27,040
Me?

216
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:29,040
I just run errands for him usually.

217
00:13:29,040 --> 00:13:31,000
Deliver letters, things like that.

218
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,560
Just routine mail.

219
00:13:32,920 --> 00:13:34,880
For slightly more important letters,

220
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:36,160
he gives them to a guy

221
00:13:36,280 --> 00:13:37,880
named Changfeng, a male prostitute.

222
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:39,560
I don't know anything else.

223
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:47,600
I wanted to use this badge to leave the city

224
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:49,560
and look for clues outside.

225
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:53,800
But since Huang Wansan has been caught by the Dragon Guard,

226
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:55,880
this badge is useless to me now.

227
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,800
Huang Wansan must be in the Imperial Prison.

228
00:13:57,800 --> 00:13:59,730
You'll definitely be implicated.

229
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:04,160
Take this badge.

230
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,920
If you give it to me, what about you?

231
00:14:06,920 --> 00:14:07,960
Don't worry.

232
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:10,530
I can handle myself.

233
00:14:11,040 --> 00:14:13,040
When I get a chance to leave the city,

234
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:14,340
I'll come find you.

235
00:14:15,560 --> 00:14:16,880
Then be careful.

236
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:18,760
Take care.

237
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:32,000
Changfeng.

238
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:34,600
Gigolo.
